query StableDiffusionQuery {

    orderBy: listing_listingId
    where: {assetContract_contains: "0x530511810d56157D50E2D215aE4fC9bC9b57df02"}
  ) {
    listingId
    listingCreator
    listing_tokenId

  newSales(
    orderBy: listingId
    where: {assetContract_contains: "0x530511810d56157D50E2D215aE4fC9bC9b57df02"}

    listingCreator
    listingId
    tokenId

  newOffers(
    orderBy: offerId
    where: {assetContract_contains: "0x530511810d56157D50E2D215aE4fC9bC9b57df02"}
  ) {
    offerId
    offeror
    offer_tokenType
    offer_totalPrice
    offer_tokenId
    offer_status
    offer_quantity
    offer_offeror
    offer_expirationTimestamp
    offer_currency
    offer_assetContract
  }
}
